Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.36,0:00:21.54,Closed,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Closed for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:41.02,News,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Hokubi News {\b0}Online \N{\c&H3F3A34&}{\fs18}Cloudy weather expected during \Nlargest meteor shower of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:01:00.00,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:36.30,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:41.76,sora-ep-title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,433)}Night of the Meteor Shower
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:38.78,sora-main-top,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:40.96,sora-main-top,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I could have cooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:42.80,sora-main-top,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:47.93,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's not burnt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:50.81,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm improving, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:54.95,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Noel, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:58.24,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Is she okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:03:02.07,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:06.70,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Next time she's here, \Nshe'll have to try my awesome cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:09.46,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:12.57,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:16.93,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I might be late tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:18.29,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:21.22,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I can contact you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:24.43,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:29.27,mailbox,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Komiya Shuichi \NKaori\N Nonoka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:26.84,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:38.40,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:42.83,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:46.12,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,There's something we need to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:54.08,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:02.26,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:15.27,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Clouds, clouds, go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.68,sora-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,I see, the olive oil—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:19.44,sora-internal,B,0000,0000,0000,,The meteor shower this year, unfortunately—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:30.30,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:34.45,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't this happen before, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:40.69,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No, it hurts more than last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:43.22,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Because I know you're forcing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:47.18,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:51.81,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet at the \Nobservatory tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:55.16,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We're all watching the \Nmeteor shower together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:58.69,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Souta, what's your plan now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:01.00,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.94,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:06.50,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:09.14,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:11.56,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:17.33,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Gathering at the observatory?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:20.95,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.04,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:27.84,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:30.18,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:34.60,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,It's what you believe, and decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.10,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:42.23,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,One more fresh ginger ale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.81,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.25,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:02.00,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make Noel smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:07.34,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,So let's all go to the \Nobservatory tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:10.01,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's watch the meteor shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:13.73,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.98,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:21.52,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you leave me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:24.07,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Don't involve yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.23,0:06:28.48,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:30.53,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:32.53,Friend,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:34.91,sora-main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:37.33,sora-main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends, please understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.46,sora-main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,You have to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:48.40,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:50.81,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:52.84,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,This girl, Yuzuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:56.08,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,loves her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:07:01.23,Friend - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,977)}Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:07:00.28,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Souta cares for his sister, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:24.33,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,When people hurt each other, \Nthis girl, Koharu, feels just as hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:37.76,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,And then, there's Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:42.24,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,She's more lonely than anyone \Nelse, yet she's stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:46.87,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,She thinks everyone will be \Nhappy so long as she endures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:53.23,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a picture of you, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:56.40,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Me? No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.47,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:01.09,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I want a picture of you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:03.85,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? Here, gimme.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.84,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:08.28,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:18.06,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,My wish is for everyone to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:23.52,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's the wish that Noel said was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:28.18,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,And it includes your smile, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:31.05,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:35.66,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:48.84,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of coming to the \Nobservatory with the others tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:51.92,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait for the meteor shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:57.22,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when they're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:06.56,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:11.07,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:15.90,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.71,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't just barge in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:28.59,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.55,0:09:32.38,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We used to be in the same room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:34.38,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:37.82,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:41.97,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Was it when I got injured \Nthat we changed rooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:47.34,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Go away already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.40,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't talk to you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.30,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:55.48,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:57.74,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:58.74,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.24,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,tougher than I thought for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.75,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.70,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,But Noel...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:11.25,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember the day \Nwe called the saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:16.30,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We had a stupid fight that morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:19.64,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:23.16,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We'd never even gotten \Ninto a fight until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:26.54,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We had no idea how to make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:30.52,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So I made a wish to the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:38.15,sora-flashbackinternal,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Please grant my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:44.91,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That I'd be friends with \Nthese guys forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:48.34,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,With you, too, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:51.92,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The saucer we saw on the dock...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:59.59,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that was Noel \Ngranting my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:01.30,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's my guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:04.28,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:07.60,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Because my wish was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:10.96,sora-flashbackinternal,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please grant my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:15.44,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,That I would be able to make up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:21.11,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,after I fight with my brother \Nor with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:27.40,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe it's our turn \Nto grant Noel's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:42.07,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:43.05,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:47.08,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,When we called the saucer, I made a wish
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:51.56,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,that we'd always be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:55.56,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I think it might be thanks to \NNoel-chan that we can still
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:59.49,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,be so close that we \Nknow how each other feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:03.99,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm borrowing this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:29.73,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:33.08,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I know they're waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.64,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,At the observatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:36.52,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:45.19,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.08,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.08,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:06.31,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:10.30,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:16.94,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione, let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:19.16,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:21.77,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to vanish, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:24.00,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to \Nsee each other anymore, will we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:26.11,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:29.19,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,how can you look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.33,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:35.88,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,You won't see Nonoka \Nand the others anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:38.38,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:41.84,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I feel
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:47.77,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,really warm here when \Nyou're all happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:52.01,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,When you're all sad, it tingles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:54.96,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,When you're all smiling,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:14:00.27,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I think I granted your wishes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:08.54,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione, let me part with my \Nbeloved friends with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:10.46,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:16.54,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Saucer-san, Saucer-san, \Nplease grant my wish
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:19.68,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,that I will always love
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:23.08,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:26.80,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,How could you refuse
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:30.22,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,after you granted my wish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:51.20,enter,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Do Not Enter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:58.34,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:08.47,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:11.34,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,She'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.22,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:15.49,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I know they're coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:35.30,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:38.80,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We just got here, too, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:40.75,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't need to give it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:43.50,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,There, there. We have tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:46.64,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, Noel-chan, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:49.50,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:52.38,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you just standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:53.91,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:04.35,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.11,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness, you're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:11.36,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:14.03,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I want you to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:25.92,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, \Nmy name is Togawa Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:16:59.20,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:06.00,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,We have some time, \Nwith the weather being how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:09.44,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:11.30,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all take pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:12.67,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:16.05,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take a ton!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:20.34,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:30.94,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:34.69,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get a good picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:37.26,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:44.06,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.21,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.62,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Smile, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:01.74,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:13.23,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:28.12,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:31.77,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:33.08,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:38.43,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cherish what you gave me forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:39.62,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:41.85,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun at the hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:43.30,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.87,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It was huge and warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:46.98,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:49.85,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.22,0:18:51.02,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:56.53,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, \NI can smile with Nonoka again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:18:59.32,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Because you watched over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:00.73,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:02.03,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:07.29,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu, I'm glad Monster-san \Nis feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:12.04,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, because you never gave up on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.30,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:20.80,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:26.34,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Monster-san got better \Nbecause you helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:27.80,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.22,0:19:31.94,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Say thanks to Souta, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:33.85,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:35.94,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:37.94,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:40.70,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:46.70,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,You and Souta made me understand \Nthe true meaning of your wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:51.05,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I said nothing but awful things,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:54.54,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,like getting rid of the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:56.64,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:01.79,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:03.76,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:16.68,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel, I'll never forget about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:19.23,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:23.76,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,You gave me lots and \Nlots of beautiful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:29.74,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.37,0:20:37.53,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:39.25,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:45.92,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I have to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:50.98,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I really, really have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:55.77,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.16,0:20:59.87,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Don't apologize, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:03.58,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:07.94,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,do you remember what \Nyour mother said?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:12.14,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:15.29,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:22.80,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:24.32,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:27.80,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki. Souta. Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:30.04,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I love you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.94,0:21:49.06,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,This is a meteor shower...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:00.84,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:03.54,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Let's watch the meteor \Nshower together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.96,0:22:07.84,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:10.63,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:13.85,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to be really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:16.95,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,You're all smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.38,0:22:20.15,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.16,0:22:23.12,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't it stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.46,0:22:25.11,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it keep overflowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:27.86,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.48,0:22:29.78,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.93,0:22:41.34,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:49.29,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.29,0:22:50.13,sora-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.54,0:22:51.68,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.92,0:22:54.99,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.21,0:23:03.04,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is she really gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.55,0:23:06.28,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:08.58,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,You were prepared, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:10.66,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but still.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.36,0:23:12.66,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,The saucer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:22.54,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you really wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:25.18,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel?
